name: Laika: Princess of Orbit
description:
A true aerospace pioneer, Laika the dog has been using the laws of gravity to fling herself from planet to planet since the 50s. After all, there's Chow to be eaten in every corner of the universe.

Created in 48 hours for KiwiJam 2020.

Sounds obtained from freesound.org users InspectorJ, TobiasKosmos, Clearwavsound and Yudena under the Creative Commons Attribution license.
